Package pec

Contains a PEC and several Events for it.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Death
    Represents a death event of an Individual.
    Event
    Represents an event.
    EventInd
    Represents an event that has an Individual that is its host.
    EventPrint
    Represents an observation event with no host.
    Move
    Represents a move event of an Individual.
    PEC
    Represents a PEC.
    Reproduction
    Represents a reproduction event of an Individual.
